2 Cryptosporidium Detection in Wild Samples in the House Mouse Hybrid Zone

Since 2016, 957 mice were sampled by this workgroup, 134 were tested for Cryptosporidium sp. by performing qPCR on DNA extracted from Ileum wall tissue. Out of these 134 samples, 134 tested positive for Crypto. An average Cryptosporidium prevalence of 100% was detected in the House Mouse Hybrid Zone.
